&lt;li&gt;Conceptualize and produce social content (still posts, GIFs, Instagram stories, etc.) as needed, including shooting, retouching, and guiding external agencies/creators&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Closely collaborate with the social team to plan content calendars, to maintain key metrics, and contribute to brainstorms to help surface new, innovative ways to create content and engage the brand’s fans/followers&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain an elevated look/feel and consistency, while partnering with cross-functional teams on understanding costs for the most impactful designs within budget&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Provide general design support on ancillary print projects, such as direct mail pieces and unexpected packaging opportunities, as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support in conceptualizing campaign visuals, as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with other creative team members during deadline crunches to complete high-profile priority projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Voraciously consume digital/social content to help the brand stay ahead of the competition&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
