&lt;li&gt;Establish department priorities, project timelines, and resource allocation to support business needs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage departmental budget, external vendor spend, and testing costs.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with executive leadership to support long-term innovation strategy and product roadmap.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent R&amp;amp;D and Product Development in cross-functional, executive, and global meetings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
