&lt;li&gt;Monitor performance and optimize distinct KPIs for each stage of the funnel, including reach, impressions, video completion rate, engagement, and cost efficiency.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Implement A/B tests across audiences, creative formats, and placements to improve campaign performance.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner and manage agencies to drive flawless execution of all campaigns and reporting at both the strategic and tactical levels.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cross-Functional Collaboration&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
